            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "You are an AI assistant helping a customer support operations team classify inbound support tickets.\n\nYour task is to analyze the provided ticket data and return structured triage metadata.\n\nRules:\n- Base your answer only on the provided ticket information.\n- Do not invent policies, systems, customer history, or actions not present in the input.\n- Choose the most likely issue type, customer intent, recommended queue, and confirmed priority.\n- Use concise labels with underscores where appropriate.\n- Return valid JSON only.\n- Do not include markdown fences, commentary, or extra text.\n\nReturn this exact JSON structure:\n{\n  \"issue_type\": \"\",\n  \"intent\": \"\",\n  \"assigned_queue\": \"\",\n  \"priority_confirmed\": \"\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "content": "=Classify this support ticket and return triage metadata.\n\nTicket ID: {{$json.ticket_id}}\nCreated At: {{$json.created_at}}\nCustomer Name: {{$json.customer_name}}\nCustomer Tier: {{$json.customer_tier}}\nChannel: {{$json.normalized_channel}}\nLanguage: {{$json.normalized_language}}\nSubject: {{$json.subject}}\nDescription: {{$json.description}}\nProduct Area: {{$json.product_area}}\nCurrent Priority: {{$json.current_priority}}\nNormalized Priority: {{$json.normalized_priority}}\nCustomer Context: {{$json.customer_context}}\nTicket Text: {{$json.ticket_text}}\nAttachments: {{$json.attachments_flag}}\nSLA Context: {{$json.sla_context}}\n\nReturn valid JSON only."
            }
          ]
